| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7277 — Recovery Inhibition (tridentlocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 264e9451-ff24-53be-85d9-e374f19ccf3a"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
